fehd.ADR_EN: G/F & M/F (PORTION), 32 ELGIN STREET, CENTRAL, HONG KONG
fehd.ADR_TC: 香港中環依利近街 32號地下及閣樓(部份)

result.adr_address: 32 Elgin St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Olive - Greek & Middle Eastern

reviews.text: Friendly service, good food, no too loud so you can have a conversation.

The food is delicious, very authentic Mediterranean style cooking! Staff is very friendly and very attentive. The atmosphere inside is very much like a South-European restaurant, great to escape from Hong Kong for a couple of hours. Giving only 4 stars because of price, I think it's at the upper limit and at the edge of too expensive.
Amazing food, Best Middle Easern in Hk, a real treat and worth the high prices. Good wine pairing. Real shame that ambience and interior are substandard, making the experience an ambiguous one.

The food was quite good, we had the halloumi to start and the duck pie. Whilst the halloumi was tasty and we'll seasoned I found it was a little bit overdone. The duck pie was delicious but a little bit dry. Good wine in stock.
Modern cool interior. Authentic Mediterranean food.
